        <InArgument x:TypeArguments="x:Int32">[If(nameExact, 1000, 0)+If(addressExact OrElse structuralAddressExact, 500, 0)+If(structuralAddressNear AndAlso Not (addressExact OrElse structuralAddressExact), 300, 0)+If(emailExact, 100, 0)+If(phoneExact, 100, 0)+identityCompleteness]</InArgument>
